Class CompanyRepUI

Object
CompanyRepUI
public class CompanyRepUI extends Object
Company representative UI. This class provides the user interface for company representatives to manage internships and applications. It adheres to the Dependency Inversion Principle (DIP) by depending on the ICompanyRepController and ILoginController abstractions.
